Follow these theming rules across the frontend:

- Use dark backgrounds with neutral borders and high-contrast text
  - Backgrounds: bg-brand-charcoal, bg-brand-charcoal-light
  - Text: text-white for headings, text-neutral-300 for body, text-neutral-400 for muted
  - Borders: border-neutral-600

- Use brand red for accents and primary actions
  - Accents: text-red-600, bg-red-600, hover:bg-red-700
  - Focus rings: focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-600 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-neutral-800

- Buttons
  - Primary: bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-all duration-200
  - Secondary: border-2 border-red-600 text-red-600 hover:bg-red-600 hover:text-white

- Forms
  - Inputs: bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-600 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-neutral-400
  - Labels: text-neutral-300 text-sm font-medium

- Layout and spacing
  - Cards: p-6 or p-8 with rounded-xl and shadow-lg + border
  - Grid: gap-6 or gap-8, grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3

